pport, field installation, and custom fabrication services. With over 100 years of product manufacturing and service delivery expertise meeting globally recognized industry standards and ISO 9001 certification, PERMA-PIPE is your best choice.<\/p><p>PERMA-PIPE has seven strategically located manufacturing facilities in the USA (2), Canada, United Arab Emirates, Saudi Arabia, Egypt, and India. PERMA-PIPE is recognized for its excellent safety record, industry-leading products and services, the highest quality fabrication, and the lowest life-cycle cost for the most complex piping systems.<\/p><p>We work with customers to provide innovative solutions for piping projects operating at all temperatures and in all environments. We have solutions for extremely low cryogenic temperatures, chilled and condensate water, and hot water and steam. For added environmental protection, we have solutions for double containment, corrosion under insulation, anti-corrosion, and leak detection. No matter what the project size or location, we are confident that our global team of technical experts and our international network can add value to your project. Please contact us to find out more.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9278e8b elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"9278e8b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"\/about\/our-history\/\" class=\"elementor-button-link elementor-button elementor-size-sm\" role=\"button\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Our Milestones<\/span>\n\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\